[30/04/2017 01:30:08] <font color="#ffffff">Todo cambia.</font>
[30/04/2017 01:30:08] <font color="#ffffff">Si ves "Natural Born Killers"...</font>
[30/04/2017 01:30:13] <font color="#ffffff">...y "Lo que el viento se llevó",</font>
